{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 407712, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "很难不赞同。我觉得新生有必要好好了解一下校内的交通安全，以及怎么骑车", "timestamp": 1601639172, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407735, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 确实！！", "timestamp": 1601639480, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407739, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "车把不要晃来晃去，变道转弯一定要打手势。新手尽量早些出门不要赶高峰", "timestamp": 1601639530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407769, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 虽然很落后，建议你清人人考一个自行车证；一大部分人是真的不会骑车，连左右行驶都能弄反（自信点，就是逆向）我也是服了", "timestamp": 1601640345, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407770, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "更正一下，大部分人不会\"骑好\"车，和后面逆向是两个断句", "timestamp": 1601640394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407771, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 反对变道转弯打手势。首先单手骑车不合规，即使短时间也是；打手势也容易误碰其他人。减速并足够明显地偏头观察安全且能让后面的人理解。", "timestamp": 1601640449, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407779, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Dave东北人，冬天泥泞路面绝对没人做敢单手转弯打手势这种危险动作。似乎这是北京特有的骑行习惯，Dave觉得并不科学；更不应该当成优越的事情炫耀。", "timestamp": 1601640614, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407839, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 老哥，打手势肯定要在转弯之前打。就跟开车打转向灯一样，要是不提前打，科三就挂了（doge", "timestamp": 1601642802, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407846, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 我也东北的，冬天压根不敢骑车", "timestamp": 1601642954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407902, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从不打手势。看好路况再拐弯又不会出问题。", "timestamp": 1601644188, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 407953, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 84403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: Dave看到的和入学被同系“学生骨干”教育的都是要伸手直到开始拐弯", "timestamp": 1601645137, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 84403, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "希望有校内媒体或者保卫处能发布或者跟进一下学堂路受伤事故的情况", "timestamp": 1601638687, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782628, "url": "", "vote": {}}}